      <body>
        <div xml:id="song31">
          <head rend="italic">Love and Musick.</head>
            <notatedMusic>
            <!-- MEI goes here -->
          </notatedMusic>
          <div type="underlay">
          <lg type="stanza">
            <l>Come my Sweet, whilst ev'ry strain</l>
            <l rend="indent1">cals our souls into the Eare,</l>
            <l>where the greedy listning fain</l>
            <l rend="indent1">would turn into the sound they heare;</l>
            <l rend="indent3">lest in desire</l>
            <l rend="indent3">to fill the quire</l>
            <l rend="indent3">themselves they tye</l>
            <l rend="indent3">to harmony,</l>
            <l>let's kiss &amp; call them back again.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
        <div>
        <lg type="stanza">
          <l>Now let's orderly convey</l>
          <l rend="indent1">Our Souls into each other's Brest,</l>
          <l>Where enterchanged let them stay</l>
          <l rend="indent1">Slumb'ring in a melting rest:</l>
          <l rend="indent3">Then with new fire</l>
          <l rend="indent3">Let them retire,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">And still present</l>
          <l rend="indent3">Sweet fresh content</l>
          <l>Youthfull as the early day.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="stanza">
          <l>Then let us a Tumult make,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">Shuffling so our souls, that we</l>
          <l>Careless who did give or take,</l>
          <l rend="indent1">May not know in whom they be,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">Then let each smother</l>
          <l rend="indent3">And stifle the other,</l>
          <l rend="indent3">Till we expire</l>
          <l rend="indent3">In gentle fire,</l>
          <l>Scorning the forgetfull Lake.</l>
        </lg>
      </div>
        </div>
